subject: failure messages
msgSnippet: Is anyone else getting these failure messages every time they send a mail to the group?  The messages start with: [005] Mail retry count exceeded sending to:
messageBody:
Is anyone else getting these failure messages every time they send a mail to
the group? The messages start with:

[005] Mail retry count exceeded sending to:
WESTPAC /NGS011

If so, is there anyway to figure out whose account this is and disable it
for the time being? I suspect what is happening is that someone's mailbox
is full and is not allowing more mail to come in.

-Jason
